de.esoco.ewt.build

Class ContainerManager<C extends Container>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.esoco.ewt.build.ContainerBuilder<C>
      • de.esoco.ewt.build.ContainerManager<C>

  • public abstract class ContainerManager<C extends Container>
extends ContainerBuilder<C>
    An abstract container builder subclass that can be used to implement the management of EWT containers. Other than ContainerBuilder this class is intended to be subclassed to create wrappers for the management of application containers.

      • buildIn

        public void buildIn(ContainerBuilder<?> rParentBuilder,
                    StyleData rStyle)
        Builds a new panel in the container of the given container builder. Invokes the methods createContainer(ContainerBuilder, StyleData) and addComponents(). The StyleData parameter must contain the necessary layout constraints for the placements of the new container in the parent.
        Parameters:
        rParentBuilder - The parent container builder to build the panel with
        rStyle - The style data for the appearance and positioning of the new container
